        +--------------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
        | .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/defaultcontext.svg | .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/bogdan-kulynych/defaultcontext.svg?branch=master |
